{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1696-06_025","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"[L’Amour &amp; la Folie, Fable]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", juin 1696 [tome 6], p. 25-31.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"#1":{"value":"Voicy un Ouvrage de Poësie dont vous ne trouverez pas le sujet nouveau, puis qu’il a déja esté traité par plusieurs personnes ; mais il y a des matieres toujours susceptibles de graces nouvelles, selon le tour heureux qu’on leur donne. La Fable qui suit est de ce nombre, &amp; M","id":"/div/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" Moreau, Avocat General en la Chambre des Comptes de Dijon, en est l’Auteur. Vous sçavez quel est son talent pour la Poësie, &amp; qu’on en peut tout attendre.","id":"/div/p/#2"}},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"value":"L’AMOUR ET LA FOLIE.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label"}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un jour le grand Maistre des Cieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Content d’un amoureux mistere,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et plus joyeux qu’à l’ordinaire,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Voulut regaler tous les Dieux.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il fit préparer l’Ambrosie,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et les mets les plus delicats,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et luy-mesme de ce repas","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ordonna la ceremonie.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par son ordre de tous costez","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mercure porta la nouvelle","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De cette feste solemnelle","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À toutes les Divinitez.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’abord chacun fit sa partie","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour y paroistre des premiers.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les deux qui vinrent les derniers,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Furent l’Amour &amp; la Folie.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour la feste de ce beau jour","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Leur presence estoit importante ;","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Car toute feste est languissante","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans la Folie &amp; sans l’Amour.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans une bonne intelligence","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On les voyoit vivre tous deux,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et mesme on remarquoit entr’eux","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Une assez juste ressemblance.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais il arriva par malheur","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’à la porte ils se rencontrerent,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que tous deux se querellerent,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et mirent le Ciel en rumeur.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le point d’honneur en fut la cause.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Amour voulut prendre le pas,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais l’autre n’y consentit pas,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et prétendit la mesme chose.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu n’entreras pas devant moy,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dit l’Amour, d’un ton de colere,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le grand Jupiter est mon Pere,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et tous les Dieux suivent ma loy.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[18]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et moy, repartit la Folie,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Moy que tu viens chercher toujours,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que ferois tu sans mon secours,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si je n’estois de la partie ?","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[20]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Comme on voit parmy nous souvent","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Précieuses, les Bourgeoises,","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Exciter de semblables noises,","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour passer dessus, ou devant.","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[22]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aprés les raisons, les injures,","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aprés les injures les coups,","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Puis on met sans dessus dessous","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Raisons, cornettes &amp; coëffures.","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[24]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De la Folie &amp; de l’Amour","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Telle fut alors la querelle,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui pour ce dernier fut cruelle,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais l’autre fit un mauvais tour.","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[26]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Comme il osa dans sa furie","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La fraper avec son carquois,","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle à l’instant avec ses doigts","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Luy creve les yeux, il s’écrie.","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[28]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et de toutes parts on entend,","id":"/div/quote/#[29]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À l’aide, au meurtre, on m’assassine,","id":"/div/quote/#[29]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si fort, que la Troupe Divine","id":"/div/quote/#[29]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Accourut à cet accident.","id":"/div/quote/#[29]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[30]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jupiter mesme en diligence","id":"/div/quote/#[31]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Y vint, laissant là le regal.","id":"/div/quote/#[31]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Amour luy découvrit son mal,","id":"/div/quote/#[31]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et le pressa pour la vangeance.","id":"/div/quote/#[31]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[32]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Folie de son costé,","id":"/div/quote/#[33]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dit ses raisons pour se défendre,","id":"/div/quote/#[33]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais à peine put-on l’entendre,","id":"/div/quote/#[33]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À voir l’Amour si maltraité.","id":"/div/quote/#[33]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[34]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Alors vint certaine Déesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[35]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que toucha ce malheur nouveau,","id":"/div/quote/#[35]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sur les yeux luy mettre un bandeau,","id":"/div/quote/#[35]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Luy marquant toute sa tendresse.","id":"/div/quote/#[35]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[36]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cependant malgré sa douleur","id":"/div/quote/#[37]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il avoit un parti contraire,","id":"/div/quote/#[37]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Car il n’est si mauvaise affaire","id":"/div/quote/#[37]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui ne trouve son défenseur.","id":"/div/quote/#[37]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[38]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je veux dire qu’en ce rencontre,","id":"/div/quote/#[39]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Comme en tous autres differends,","id":"/div/quote/#[39]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On se partagea sur les rangs,","id":"/div/quote/#[39]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’un estoit pour, l’autre estoit contre.","id":"/div/quote/#[39]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[40]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les uns soutenoient que l’Amour","id":"/div/quote/#[41]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Devoit préceder sa partie,","id":"/div/quote/#[41]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’autres tenant pour la Folie,","id":"/div/quote/#[41]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Condamnoient l’Amour à leur tour.","id":"/div/quote/#[41]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[42]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enfin, Jupiter en bon Pere","id":"/div/quote/#[43]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Accorda ce long démeslé,","id":"/div/quote/#[43]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et dit à l’Amour désolé,","id":"/div/quote/#[43]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ces mots qui finirent l’affaire.","id":"/div/quote/#[43]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[44]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Puis qu’il faut qu’à vivre sans yeux","id":"/div/quote/#[45]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Folie ainsi te réduise,","id":"/div/quote/#[45]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je veux qu’en tout temps, en tous lieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[45]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce soit elle qui te conduise.","id":"/div/quote/#[45]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[46]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ainsi dit, ainsi fait, &amp; c’est depuis ce jour","id":"/div/quote/#[47]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que par tout la Folie accompagne l’Amour.","id":"/div/quote/#[47]/lg/l[1]/#"}}]}}]}}}